name: Tie fighter - Defenders of space
description:
Tie Fighter - Defenders of space
Highly retro classic game with addictive gameplay and music that will bring you back to the 80´s in a jiffy.
One touch / slide gameplay, take out the enemies and earn coins and space respect in order to defeat the evil eyes that are hidden in the dark space.
Only the space lords of Tie Fighters can defeat the dark order.

Highly addictive for any arcade game fan.
